parameters:
\nc<Security>Now, we will guide those who failed to meet their quarterly
quotas to their dispatch locations.

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>(Ah, they're here...\[bustMsgExp[1, 3]] But Meary-senpai said
she would take care of it, so I should be fine...)

\nc<Security>Saki-san. You are a subject for forced dispatch due to
insufficient achievements.
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>What?! Wait a minute, please! Isn't there some mistake...?
\nc<Guard 2>Why does everyone say the same thing...
\nc<Saki>Se, Senpai! What on earth is going on?

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>If Saki were to run away, we would all suffer the
consequences, you know.

\nc<Senpai>The entire building is sealed on the day of the quarterly
performance announcement, so I figured you wouldn't be able
to escape anyway...

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>It's not that Saki betrayed me. I just assumed you would
naturally handle something as basic as the quarterly
achievements.

\nc<Senpai>It's not hell, it's forced dispatch. You'll do your best
there too, won't you, Saki?
